        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks HTS for <hi rend="italic">Entomologist’s Weekly Intelligencer</hi> [no. 2, 12 Apr 1856]. Agrees with his remarks [in "Why did Mr Westwood get the Royal Medal?"], but explains that a change in rules for awarding the Royal Medal has been made. Earlier it had to be given for publications in <hi rend="italic">Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society</hi>, which explains small number of entomologist recipients.</p> 
        </abstract>
